OL,3,CDoctors warn of 'demoralising and
OL,4,Cunsafe' conditions in Northern Ireland
OL,5,CEDs
OL,7,FDoctors have warned of "unsafe"
OL,8,Fconditions and an "all-time low" for
OL,9,Fmorale across emergency departments in
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,12,FAll clinicians who responded to a
OL,13,Fsurvey published by the Royal College
OL,14,Fof Emergency Medicine (RCEM) on
OL,15,FWednesday found that patients are
OL,16,Fcoming to harm amid overcrowded
OL,17,Fconditions at emergency departments
OL,18,F(EDs).
OL,26,@oD@XOUoD@_O]pD@SOUpD@`O]
