OL,3,CDoctors warn of 'demoralising and
OL,4,Cunsafe' conditions in Northern Ireland
OL,5,CEDs
OL,7,FLead consultants in all nine major EDs
OL,8,Fcompleted a "snapshot" poll last
OL,9,FMonday to capture the situation in A&E.
OL,11,FThe poll found that across all nine
OL,12,FEDs, 401 people were waiting for
OL,13,Finpatient beds and nearly half of
OL,14,Fthese patients (49%) were receiving
OL,15,Fcare in a non-designated space such as
OL,16,Fa corridor, the floor or on a chair.
OL,26,@pD@MOUpD@VO]
