OL,3,CDoctors warn of 'demoralising and
OL,4,Cunsafe' conditions in Northern Ireland
OL,5,CEDs
OL,7,FThe ED cubicle occupancy of patients
OL,8,Fwaiting for an inpatient bed was at
OL,9,F137%, with one patient waiting in the
OL,10,FED for 124 hours when the data was
OL,11,Frecorded ` equivalent to more than
OL,12,Ffive days.
OL,14,FAll clinicians who responded believe
OL,15,Fthat patients are coming to harm in
OL,16,Fthe current conditions.
OL,18,FEvery department reported that a major
OL,19,Freason for overcrowding was delayed
OL,20,Fdischarges due to a lack of social
OL,21,Fcare arrangements.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/13
