OL,3,CDoctors warn of 'demoralising and
OL,4,Cunsafe' conditions in Northern Ireland
OL,5,CEDs
OL,7,FOne respondent stated their ED was
OL,8,Fabove capacity with "no resuscitation
OL,9,Fspace, 10-hour waits at the front
OL,10,Fdoor, and ambulance offloads waiting
OL,11,Feight hours", adding "it feels frankly
OL,12,Funsafe".
OL,14,FAnother said morale amongst staff "is
OL,15,Fat an all-time low; people dread
OL,16,Fcoming to work because they cannot
OL,17,Fdeliver the high standard of care we
OL,18,Fstrive for and staff feel vulnerable
OL,19,Fand exposed".
