OL,3,CDoctors warn of 'demoralising and
OL,4,Cunsafe' conditions in Northern Ireland
OL,5,CEDs
OL,7,FRCEM's vice president for Northern
OL,8,FIreland, Dr Michael Perry, said the
OL,9,Fsituation in EDs "put simply, is just
OL,10,Fawful".
OL,12,FHe said: "Our members and their
OL,13,Fcolleagues are putting on their scrubs
OL,14,Fevery day knowing that they will be
OL,15,Ftrying their best to deliver quality
OL,16,Fcare in spaces that were never
OL,17,Fdesigned for care to be delivered in `
OL,18,Fon trolleys in corridors, chairs and
OL,19,Feven, shamefully, on the floor.
OL,26,@qD@ROUrD@FO]tD@JOU
