OL,3,CDoctors warn of 'demoralising and
OL,4,Cunsafe' conditions in Northern Ireland
OL,5,CEDs
OL,7,F"These are patients, who are arriving
OL,8,Fto our EDs, who are vulnerable, sick
OL,9,Fand in need of care. Yet they are
OL,10,Fenduring these conditions for hours
OL,11,Fand hours and hours. And as this
OL,12,Fsurvey reveals, for some, it leads
OL,13,Finto days.
OL,15,F"It's not just degrading, and
OL,16,Fdemoralising ` this is where the harm
OL,17,Flies. Last year, there were 1,122
OL,18,Fdeaths associated with long A&E waits
OL,19,Fin our country.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/13
