OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F441A1765990012
OL,3,CDoctors warn of 'demoralising and
OL,4,Cunsafe' conditions in Northern Ireland
OL,5,CEDs
OL,7,F"These are people, loved ones. I fear
OL,8,Fwhat this number will be for 2025.
OL,10,F"All of this is a symptom of the
OL,11,Fsystem not functioning as it should.
OL,12,FWe can't move patients out of our
OL,13,Fdepartments because there's a lack of
OL,14,Favailable ward beds for them to be
OL,15,Fmoved to, meaning they become stuck.
OL,17,F"Are walls aren't elastic, so people
OL,18,Fend up in areas where they should
OL,19,Fnever be receiving care in or stuck in
OL,20,Fambulances waiting to even get through
OL,21,Four doors.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/13
