OL,3,CDoctors warn of 'demoralising and
OL,4,Cunsafe' conditions in Northern Ireland
OL,5,CEDs
OL,7,F"We cannot go on like this. RCEM has
OL,8,Fmade a series of urgent
OL,9,Frecommendations to the Northern
OL,10,FIreland Executive, including the need
OL,11,Fto spread responsibility for patient
OL,12,Fflow across the hospital network, to
OL,13,Fbring back a healthcare system that we
OL,14,Fonce were proud of."
OL,16,FA spokesperson for the Department of
OL,17,FHealth said it accepts the findings of
OL,18,Fthe survey, adding that the services
OL,19,Fare under more severe pressure in the
OL,20,Fwintertime.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@TO]
