OL,3,CDoctors warn of 'demoralising and
OL,4,Cunsafe' conditions in Northern Ireland
OL,5,CEDs
OL,7,F"No-one wants to see sick people being
OL,8,Ftreated in corridors but sadly, we
OL,9,Fhave a finite capacity, and severe
OL,10,Fpressures arise when hospitals are
OL,11,Fforced to operate often well beyond
OL,12,Fcapacity," the statement said.
OL,14,F"Staff are doing their best 24 hours a
OL,15,Fday, seven days a week, often in very
OL,16,Fdifficult situations to try and
OL,17,Falleviate those pressures and give the
OL,18,Fbest care they can.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@JO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/13
