OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F441A1765990012
OL,3,CDoctors warn of 'demoralising and
OL,4,Cunsafe' conditions in Northern Ireland
OL,5,CEDs
OL,7,F"Unfortunately, it is a complex
OL,8,Fproblem and there is no quick fix but
OL,9,Fthe only medium to long-term solution
OL,10,Fis to reduce demand.
OL,12,F"That means reducing the number of
OL,13,Fpeople coming through ED doors but
OL,14,Falso focusing on flow, which means
OL,15,Fgetting people out of hospital as soon
OL,16,Fas they are fit for discharge in order
OL,17,Fto free up beds for those coming
OL,18,Fbehind.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/13
