OL,3,CDoctors warn of 'demoralising and
OL,4,Cunsafe' conditions in Northern Ireland
OL,5,CEDs
OL,7,F"We are also conscious that these
OL,8,Fproblems are presenting across the UK
OL,9,Fand reflect a wider issue with the way
OL,10,Fin which health systems are able to
OL,11,Fmanage demand for care by meeting
OL,12,Fpeople's needs in community settings
OL,13,Fand enabling patients to return home
OL,14,Fsafely when fit for discharge.
OL,16,F"This is why in Northern Ireland we
OL,17,Fhave undertaken two significant pieces
OL,18,Fof work this year.
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU
