OL,3,CDoctors warn of 'demoralising and
OL,4,Cunsafe' conditions in Northern Ireland
OL,5,CEDs
OL,7,F"The first involves taking action to
OL,8,Fhelp manage our frail elderly patients
OL,9,Fbetter and keep them away from
OL,10,Fhospitals.
OL,12,F"The second, our Reset Plan, is
OL,13,Fattempting over the next three years
OL,14,Fto refocus our work towards earlier
OL,15,Fsupport and intervention, prevention,
OL,16,Fproviding neighbourhood-based care and
OL,17,Fencouraging people to take more
OL,18,Fresponsibility for their own health on
OL,19,Fa routine basis.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU
