OL,3,CDoctors warn of 'demoralising and
OL,4,Cunsafe' conditions in Northern Ireland
OL,5,CEDs
OL,7,F"We recognise however that this will
OL,8,Ftake time to impact, and it is not
OL,9,Fhelped by the very challenging
OL,10,Ffinancial position we face in Northern
OL,11,FIreland presently.
OL,13,F"But in the interim, we will continue
OL,14,Fto manage the quality of care we are
OL,15,Fable to provide to the best effect."
